                  --_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--
                        Balanced Tree (AVL)
                  --_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--

Use:
  'make' to compile.
  'make clean' to remove the objects.
  './avl' to execute.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Commands:
  'i' to insert a new node.
  'd' to delete a node.
  'p' to print the tree.
  'e' to exit.

  OBS: All commands without ''.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Inserting a new node:
  Enter the value of the new node (use integer type).
  Example: 20.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Deleting a node:
  Enter the value of the node (use integer type).
  Example: 20.
